Steps to Run the SmallBizz Project:

1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/shravani-sajekar/SmallBizz

2. Install Dependencies
Navigate to the project folder and install the required Node.js dependencies:

cd SmallBizz
npm install

3. Run the Project
Start the project using nodemon (ensure it is installed globally or as a project dependency):

nodemon app.js